		title: "Strawberry"
		icon: {id: "pamhc2crops:strawberryitem", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Strawberry bushes grow wild in forest biomes as low ground-cover plants; right-click the bush to harvest without uprooting it, then replant seeds on Rich Soil for a permanent bed.", "Strawberries are a core Pam's ingredient across jams, fruit pies, berry mixes, and smoothies — plant a large patch early, as demand across the full recipe library is high."]
