		title: "Blueberry"
		icon: {id: "pamhc2crops:blueberryitem", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Blueberry bushes grow wild in forest and taiga biomes; right-click to harvest without breaking the plant, same as strawberries, and replant seeds on Rich Soil to establish a cultivated bed.", "Used in Pam's blueberry jam, muffins, pies, and mixed berry recipes — a small automated blueberry bed removes this ingredient from the manual-gathering loop entirely."]
