		title: "Raspberry"
		icon: {id: "pamhc2crops:raspberryitem", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Raspberry canes grow along forest edges and open thickets; right-click to harvest without uprooting the bush, then replant seeds on standard farmland or Rich Soil.", "Raspberries appear in Pam's berry jams, mixed fruit pies, and dessert recipes — combining them with Strawberries and Blueberries covers most of the mixed-berry recipe set."]
