		description: ["Cranberry plants grow wild near wet and swampy biomes as low ground bushes; right-click to harvest without uprooting, and replant seeds on farmland close to water.", "Essential for cranberry sauce, juice, and tart baked goods in Pam's recipe library — their high sourness makes them a distinct flavor category from other berries and they cannot be substituted."]
