		description: ["Tomato plants grow wild in plains and savannah biomes as vine crops; Pam's tomatoes and Farmer's Delight tomatoes are interchangeable in recipes, so whichever you grow first covers both mods.", "Appears in an enormous range of dishes: Pasta with Tomato Sauce, Tomato Salad, cooked Farmer's Delight preparations, and as the base for every sauce and stew that needs acidity. Grow in bulk."]
