		description: ["Grape vines grow on warm hillsides and farmland; plant seeds and the vine produces grape clusters on the plant block when fully mature.", "Used in Pam's jelly, juice, fruit salad, and wine-adjacent recipes — growing a dedicated grape bed is worthwhile because grapes appear across multiple recipe categories."]
